th </div><div class="t m2dd x45 h35 y6e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the faithful of all ages when he said, </div><div class="t m7cc x45 h35 y1a0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Their way of thinking I can&apos;t accept&quot; </div><div class="t m575 x45 h35 y216 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(verse 16, TEV). </div><div class="t ma49 xbc h35 ydec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This passage also verified Job&apos;s basic </div><div class="t m1a4 x45 h35 y5fc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reliance upon God. In his </div><div class="t me5 x45 h35 y24d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">discouragement, he may have </div><div class="t m11b x45 h35 y6f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complained and questioned, but his </div><div class="t m416 x20 h35 y28c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">basic loyalty was unimpaired. It is </div><div class="t ma8c x20 h35 y12b9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">important to distinguish in any life </div><div class="t m649 x20 h35 y95 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">between the varying moods created by </div><div class="t m41e x20 h35 y18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changing circumstances and the </div><div class="t m65c x20 h35 y1dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">underlying commitments that are </div><div class="t m8e1 x20 h35 yac7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unaffected by the fortunes of life. </div><div class="t mf63 x20 h32 y5e5 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m7a0 x20 h32 y5bb ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1692 x56 h32 y84d ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Please Listen!&quot; </div><div class="t ma23 x56 h32 y36b ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 21:1-3) </div><div class="t mec2 x20 h32 y970 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m8b3 x56 h32 y273 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why Do Wicked Prosper? </div><div class="t mdd1 x56 h32 y3c2 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 21:7-13) </div><div class="t m2ca x20 h32 y222 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m105d x56 h32 y295 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Wasted Advice </div><div class="t m19e x56 h32 y5f1 ff1 